1.00	Die_t%C3%B6dlichen_W%C3%BCnsche	Die tödlichen Wünsche	Die tödlichen Wünsche, op.27, is an opera by Giselher Klebe who also wrote the libretto based on La peau de chagrin by Honoré de Balzac. It consists of fifteen lyrical scenes in three acts.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/2/21/Giselher_Klebe_2008.jpg/220px-Giselher_Klebe_2008.jpg
